      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the highly sought-after 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant delivers a linear 385hp, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-fitted limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) calibration, offering precise damping and cornering geometry with zero bushing deflection. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the vehicle shows no signs of bore scoring or IMS issues, and the undercarriage remains concours-clean. This is a mechanically superlative example, offering the raw feedback and analog engagement synonymous with the pinnacle of the 911 lineage.",
